
### Créer une session de paiement (remplacer TOKEN et COMMANDE_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/paiements/creer-session
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "commandeId": "COMMANDE_ID"
}

### Confirmer un paiement (simulation)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/paiements/confirmer
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "paymentIntentId": "pi_123456789"
}

### Récupérer l'historique des paiements
GET http://localhost:5000/api/paiements
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Webhook Stripe (test avec Stripe CLI)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/paiements/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Stripe-Signature: whsec_test_signature

{
    "id": "evt_test_webhook",
    "object": "event",
    "type": "payment_intent.succeeded",
    "data": {
        "object": {
            "id": "pi_123456789",
            "object": "payment_intent",
            "amount": 2000,
            "currency": "eur",
            "status": "succeeded"
        }
    }
}